1. Data Collection
This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data, browsing data, or user identifiers. All processing is performed entirely within your local browser.

2. Use of Permissions
The extension requests permission only to access https://chat.openai.com/ in order to inject a local sidebar. These permissions are used strictly to enable functionality and do not involve data extraction or communication with external servers.

3. No Cookies or Tracking
We do not use cookies, analytics, trackers, or third-party services. Your interactions stay entirely on your device.

4. Compliance with GDPR and U.S. Privacy Laws
